tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T18:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩為之放低？<br />\n唔影響我日常生活既心情但無心機拍長拖<br />\n每次有女埋身我都知我內心未放得低<br />\n<br />\n其實佢都想同翻我一齊<br />\n但我好清楚我地唔適合大家<br />\n<br />\n係咪慘過放唔低？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭一段，一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最斃我已經知佢無野係值得我留戀同返轉頭<br />\n外表又唔係，內涵又唔係，性格又唔係，又唔係對我特別好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係我附出左好多感情收唔番<br />\n<br />\n只能講佢喺最特別既時候遇上條件最差既我<br />\n庸人自擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531d5c9e83c057de53cc1302f46aeaa31016e14f","tid":44673,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲好掛住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時會忍唔住睇返佢啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚會唔記得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔記得咪仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為仲鐘意<br />\n先唔想忘記</blockquote><br />\n你鍾意有撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地理撚得你死<br />\n同新仔日屌夜屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88aa752772f3f582b4770b96aae5afb53c844ae0","tid":44673,"uid":62695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:28:31.000Z","msg":"今日岩岩好散左一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲未放得低"},{"pid":"82f6fc6ec43f9427f12ab5615ad2d8f10c0507b9","tid":44673,"uid":54796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T23