ke.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df7c8a1400c8f5cc9bcf24bfb4238bd2815e9e2","tid":44673,"uid":34132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:10:31.000Z","msg":"好驚自己要用幾年時間先放得低"},{"pid":"e03e7469669f28bb06b5b90994054dca231600b4","tid":44673,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"半個月<br />\n因為越遲move on<br />\n越遲get ready 去擁有一個 mr.right"},{"pid":"fb5111bb1390692bca44ac5b7b18736292c2b372","tid":44673,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:15:15.000Z","msg":"唔知算唔算放低左<br />\n散左3年幾就4年<br />\n但唔敢再拍拖<br />\n好驚又散之後又sad幾年"},{"pid":"1646cc887792d176eac452778e599b65d01e745b","tid":44673,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"唔放低了<br />\n反正都無左你 下半世點過都無所謂"},{"pid":"2e0e60603fae04e5d31638c4200032beb392cd17","tid":44673,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:18:58.000Z","msg":"我初戀 拍左三年幾<br />\n用半個月恢復<br />\n一啲留戀感覺都無！<br />\n<br />\n繼續留戀一個同你生命再無關係既人<br />\n會令 追緊你 或者對你有興趣既人 卻步<br />\n<br />\n我唔會咁傻<br />\n我好深信遇到既下一個比起人渣初戀成熟 同埋條件好好多"},{"pid":"48b94b7e725f4d2b1a4de113d7674408e7cbe852","tid":44673,"uid":58947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:25:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我初戀 拍左三年幾<br />\n用半個月恢復<br />\n一啲留戀感覺都無！<br />\n<br />\n繼續留戀一個同你生命再無關係既人<br />\n會令 追緊你 或者對你有興趣既人 卻步<br />\n<br />\n我唔會咁傻<br />\n我好深信遇到既下一個比起人渣初戀成熟 同埋條件好好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜自己衝破唔到自己的關口"},{"pid":"095c56cc50cd365905fde7f3616938df7fc184f8","tid":44673,"uid":68301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"同ex分開四五年  同現任兩年，可以話你聽放唔底，，還愛你  帶一點恨，，，但又恨唔洛，，全部都係雞黎，，但你會願意包起佢"},{"pid":"d9534a0ac1336d2d7a18ff1ccb274d9509cd1294","tid":44673,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我初戀 拍左三年幾<br />\n用半個月恢復<br />\n一啲留戀感覺都無！<br />\n<br />\n繼續留戀一個同你生命再無關係既人<br />\n會令 追緊你 或者對你有興趣既人 卻步<br />\n<br />\n我唔會咁傻<br />\n我好深信遇到既下一個比起人渣初戀成熟 同埋條件好好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜自己衝破唔到自己的關口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你需要一個朋友/屋企人鬧醒你<br />\n我都係俾屋企人一句on9鬧落黎<br />\n慢慢先識醒"},{"pid":"77e300cbfd2e0a276f6c1a7b8989f65425a6b603","tid":44673,"uid":60834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:40:37.000Z","msg":"起碼一年<br />\n好多時候都以為自己放得低<br />\n但係一寂寞就會久唔久都諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e783ff27328bb38a5f095e3c232c458a721df62","tid":44673,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T18:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時分唔清  究竟係放唔低個ex  定係放唔低啲回憶</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5408c7d782653630a4ff6615c80488b9b6a6422f","tid":44673,"uid":53405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/004412_8c4b9b860ea467425eb7980060225d8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F004412_8c4b9b860ea467425eb7980060225d8f.jpg&h=cc74722f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n句野睇到我眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b5b773a57217e2a3c0bcaffd82d79806d86d48","tid":44673,"uid":64609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22